{"tid":1637404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家係唔係忽略咗一個香城online 職業-講故佬","createTime":"2019-10-08T03:32:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T03:38:51.000Z","uid":260085,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"cb35775dad5050d112b9fb65c053631c7e124725","tid":1637404,"uid":260085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:32:16.000Z","msg":"搭車，排隊，行街又或者茶餐廳食飯時同friend 傾下時政/傾電話，一唔小心講得太大聲，可能就會被隔離阿婆阿伯聽到晒。<br />\n<br />\n例如排緊巴士/党鐵時，會有friend無端端打電話問到咗未？我就會大大聲答<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">仆街党鐵為害示威者，又專登封站啊!<br />\n我仲趕住去銀行，再遲d錢就被人㩒到無晒啦。</span><br />\n<br />\n大家自由發揮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec7d137ab6e8245fe1ad1f00fd55001ca65d034","tid":1637404,"uid":260085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"講<span style=\"color: red;\">古</span>佬"},{"pid":"36ffb30eb931119178a39dd76a6feff60e2f1e01","tid":1637404,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec7d137ab6e8245fe1ad1f00fd55001ca65d034","tid":1637404,"uid":260085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"講<span style=\"color: red;\">古</span>佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"點解係用古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03979ab4ebd646bd5fedaae0542acf12fa4063a","tid":1637404,"uid":260085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"36ffb30eb931119178a39dd76a6feff60e2f1e01","tid":1637404,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec7d137ab6e8245fe1ad1f00fd55001ca65d034","tid":1637404,"uid":260085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:35:01.000Z","msg":"講<span style=\"color: red;\">古</span>佬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"點解係用古<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T03:37:55.000Z","msg":"中文差，答唔到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/